 InstallPackages←{
     ⍝ Install packages in project folder ⍵
     prj_dir←⊃1 ⎕NPARTS ⍵,'/'
     rc msg tree←ReadDepTree prj_dir
     rc≠0:rc msg

     pkgs_dir←prj_dir,'packages/'
     rc←3 ⎕NDELETE pkgs_dir
     rc←3 ⎕MKDIR pkgs_dir

     tgts←pkgs_dir∘,¨tree.id
     rcs msgs src_dirs←↓⍉↑GetPackage¨tree.id
     ∨/rcs≠0:1 'Failed getting packages'
     r←src_dirs CreateSymbolicLink¨tgts
     0 ''
 }
